examples.en: I went to the game with my posse.

examples.en: She was met at the airport by a posse of reporters.

examples.en: The sheriff and his posse rode out to look for the bandits.
examples.ru: Шериф и его отряд поехали искать этих бандитов.

examples.en: I was surrounded by a posse of photographers.
